WEBVTT

01:46.000 --> 01:48.500
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:48.500 --> 01:51.083
Man: TWO TREASURE HUNTERS MADE
A GHASTLY DISCOVERY TODAY

01:51.083 --> 01:52.750
WHEN THEY STUMBLED
ON WHAT APPEARS TO BE

01:52.750 --> 01:57.208
AN UNDERWATER GRAVEYARD IN A
CREVICE OFF THE COAST OF MIAMI.

01:57.208 --> 01:58.917
Debra: DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS?

01:58.917 --> 02:01.417
MEANS THERE MIGHT BE
A NEW MASS MURDERER OUT THERE,

02:01.417 --> 02:03.250
WAY WORSE THAN
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

02:03.250 --> 02:04.959
THE "BAY HARBOR BUTCHER"?

02:04.959 --> 02:07.291
THAT'S WHAT THE PRESS IS CALLING
WHOEVER DUMPED BODIES OFFSHORE.

02:07.291 --> 02:09.667
THE LAST THING MIAMI NEEDS
IS ANOTHER SERIAL KILLER.

02:09.667 --> 02:12.333
13 AND COUNTING.

02:12.333 --> 02:13.667
THEY'RE SO SWAMPED UP THERE,

02:13.667 --> 02:15.583
THEY HAD TO BRING IN
OUTSIDE TALENT.

02:15.583 --> 02:16.709
Doakes: FRANK LUNDY?

02:16.709 --> 02:18.375
THE GREEN RIVER KILLER,
THE D.C. SNIPER --

02:18.375 --> 02:20.625
IF THE CASE WAS IMPOSSIBLE,
HE BROKE IT.

02:20.625 --> 02:23.458
Dexter:
SO, THIS IS THE MAN WHO STANDS
BETWEEN ME AND DEATH ROW.

02:23.458 --> 02:26.375
WITH YOUR HELP, WE'LL FIND
WHOEVER DID THIS AWFUL THING.

02:26.375 --> 02:28.917
SO, LET'S GET A JUMP-START
ON THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

02:28.917 --> 02:30.208
WITH DOAKES TAILING ME,

02:30.208 --> 02:32.583
MY LIFE'S BEEN ALL JEKYLL
AND NO HYDE.

02:32.583 --> 02:34.917
PAUL KEPT INSISTING TO ME

02:34.917 --> 02:37.917
THAT YOU KNOCKED HIM
OVER THE HEAD,

02:37.917 --> 02:40.458
DRAGGED HIM TO HIS MOTEL,
AND SHOT HIM UP WITH DRUGS.

02:40.458 --> 02:42.750
I HIT PAUL TO PROTECT YOU
AND THE KIDS.

02:42.750 --> 02:44.959
LOOK, IF THERE IS ANYTHING LEFT
BETWEEN US,

02:44.959 --> 02:46.709
YOU WILL ANSWER ME
THIS ONE QUESTION

02:46.709 --> 02:50.834
AND YOU WILL TELL ME
THE TRUTH.

02:50.834 --> 02:54.333
ARE YOU AN ADDICT?

02:54.333 --> 02:56.625
YES, I HAVE AN ADDICTION.

03:10.250 --> 03:12.500
MY NAME IS CAROLINE.

03:12.500 --> 03:13.834
I'M AN ADDICT.

03:13.834 --> 03:15.417
All: HI, CAROLINE.

03:15.417 --> 03:18.875
Caroline:
UM, I STARTED TAKING PAIN PILLS

03:18.875 --> 03:21.500
AFTER MY BACK SURGERY.

03:21.500 --> 03:25.000
I DON'T NEED THEM
FOR THE PAIN ANYMORE.

03:25.000 --> 03:27.250
NOW I...

03:27.250 --> 03:29.208
NOW I JUST NEED THEM.

03:29.208 --> 03:31.625
AND I NEED DUCT TAPE --
THREE OR FOUR ROLLS.

03:31.625 --> 03:34.542
RUNNING LOW
ON HEAVY-DUTY TRASH BAGS.

03:34.542 --> 03:37.583
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
I SHARPENED MY KNIVES?

03:37.583 --> 03:39.625
[ Voice breaking ]
AND I LOST MY LICENSE.

03:39.625 --> 03:40.834
TEARS NOW?

03:40.834 --> 03:42.750
IT'S VERY HARD
TO CONCENTRATE IN HERE.

03:42.750 --> 03:44.709
HOW AM I SUPPOSED
TO GET ANY WORK DONE?

03:44.709 --> 03:46.417
[ SNIFFS ]

03:46.417 --> 03:50.750
MY HUSBAND SAYS HE'S GONNA LEAVE
ME IF I DON'T STAY SOBER.

03:53.208 --> 03:55.542
BUT I HAVE TO DO THIS
FOR MYSELF.

03:55.542 --> 03:59.166
"NO SELF-CONTROL, LOST
EVERYTHING, TRYING TO STOP."

03:59.166 --> 04:02.250
SAME WHINY STORY
OVER AND OVER FOR...

04:02.250 --> 04:04.667
10 MINUTES --
FEELS LIKE 10 HOURS.

04:04.667 --> 04:10.709
...TAKING LORTABS
AND DARVOCET AND PERCOCET

04:10.709 --> 04:12.834
AND ANYTHING
I COULD GET MY HANDS ON.

04:12.834 --> 04:16.458
AND EVEN NOW...

04:16.458 --> 04:19.291
I'D KILL FOR A VICODIN.

04:19.291 --> 04:20.625
LIGHTWEIGHT.

04:20.625 --> 04:24.625
FIRST I THOUGHT, "NARCOTICS
ANONYMOUS," I DON'T BELONG HERE.

04:24.625 --> 04:26.750
YOU GUYS ARE REAL ADDICTS.

04:26.750 --> 04:28.458
[ LIGHT LAUGHTER ]

04:28.458 --> 04:31.417
Rita: SO, HOW WAS THE MEETING?
TELL ME EVERYTHING.

04:31.417 --> 04:33.375
IT WAS, UH, INTERESTING,

04:33.375 --> 04:35.542
HEARING THE SAME STORY
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

04:35.542 --> 04:37.667
KNOWING
YOU'RE NOT ALONE.
EXACTLY.

04:37.667 --> 04:40.125
DID YOU GET FORTUNE COOKIES?

04:40.125 --> 04:42.083
ONLY THE ONES
WITH THE GOOD FORTUNES.

04:42.083 --> 04:44.875
SO, DID YOU SHARE
OR JUST LISTEN?

04:44.875 --> 04:47.875
I JUST WANTED TO TAKE IT ALL IN
MY FIRST TIME OUT.

04:47.875 --> 04:49.291
THINK THEY FORGOT...

04:49.291 --> 04:51.583
AH, HERE THEY ARE.
SPRING ROLLS.

04:51.583 --> 04:54.291
AND WHAT ABOUT A SPONSOR?
DID YOU FIND ONE?

04:54.291 --> 04:56.709
I DIDN'T WANT TO RUSH
INTO ANYTHING.

04:56.709 --> 04:58.792
IT'S AN IMPORTANT
RELATIONSHIP.

04:58.792 --> 05:00.625
ABSOLUTELY.

05:00.625 --> 05:03.208
OKAY, SO, LET'S SEE
YOUR NEWCOMER'S CHIP.

05:03.208 --> 05:05.333
[ SIGHS ]
NEWCOMER'S CHIP.

05:05.333 --> 05:08.291
YEAH...
[ SIGHS ]

05:08.291 --> 05:11.834
YOU DID STAY UNTIL THE END,
DIDN'T YOU?

05:11.834 --> 05:15.458
OF COURSE I DID.
RIGHT TO THE END.

05:15.458 --> 05:17.041
[ SCOFFS ]

05:17.041 --> 05:19.500
YOU'RE A TERRIBLE LIAR.

05:22.291 --> 05:25.458
I KNOW TOO MUCH
ABOUT 12-STEP PROGRAMS

05:25.458 --> 05:28.125
TO BE EASILY CONNED,
DEXTER.

05:28.125 --> 05:31.000
I DIDN'T STAY TILL THE END  END,
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU MEAN.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.959
I HAD SOME IMPORTANT ERRANDS
TO RUN.

05:32.959 --> 05:34.333
MMM.
IMPORTANT?

05:34.333 --> 05:38.166
WHAT? AM I IMPORTANT?
ARE THE KIDS?

05:38.166 --> 05:40.000
YEAH.

05:40.000 --> 05:41.583
YES, OF COURSE.

05:41.583 --> 05:44.583
WELL, YOU'RE JUST GONNA HAVE
TO FIGURE OUT HOW IMPORTANT,

05:44.583 --> 05:46.458
BECAUSE IF YOU DON'T WORK
THE PROGRAM --

05:46.458 --> 05:48.917
AND I MEAN REALLY  WORK IT --
I JUST...

05:48.917 --> 05:50.458
I CAN'T GO THROUGH THIS
AGAIN.

05:52.959 --> 05:54.875
ALL RIGHT, KIDS.
DINNER.

05:54.875 --> 05:57.125
HOW IMPORTANT ARE THEY?

05:57.125 --> 06:00.625
I'M SURE SOMEONE WITH A HEART
COULD ANSWER THAT QUESTION.

06:08.250 --> 06:11.625
TOMORROW.
I'LL GO TOMORROW.

06:11.625 --> 06:13.375
I'LL STAY.

06:16.417 --> 06:17.375
OKAY.

06:17.375 --> 06:19.542
OKAY?
OKAY.

06:22.375 --> 06:24.166
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

06:24.166 --> 06:25.667
HOLD THE ELEVATOR!

06:28.875 --> 06:30.166
[ SIGHS ]

06:32.000 --> 06:34.417
THANKS.

06:35.583 --> 06:39.417
NICE DODGE LAST NIGHT, FLOORING
IT THROUGH THAT YELLOW LIGHT.

06:39.417 --> 06:41.834
OH...

06:41.834 --> 06:43.667
WERE YOU BEHIND ME?

06:45.250 --> 06:47.041
SEE YOU TONIGHT.

06:47.041 --> 06:50.375
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

06:50.375 --> 06:52.875
LaGuerta:
WE WILL GET TO ALL OF YOU.

06:52.875 --> 06:54.458
OKAY, TAKE THEIR NAMES

06:54.458 --> 06:56.792
AND KEEP THEM OUT OF THE BULLPEN
TILL WE FIGURE THIS OUT.

06:56.792 --> 07:00.375
Man: SUE MacMILLAN.
SHE DISAPPEARED FOUR YEARS AGO.

07:00.375 --> 07:02.166
WHO ARE THEY?

07:02.166 --> 07:03.709
Batista:
EVERY FAMILY MEMBER

07:03.709 --> 07:06.625
OF EVERY MISSING PERSON
FOR THE LAST DECADE.

07:06.625 --> 07:09.291
INCLUDING SOME SAD, LONELY,
AND PRESUMABLY SINGLE WOMEN,

07:09.291 --> 07:10.959
COURTESY
OF LIEUTENANT PASCAL.

07:10.959 --> 07:13.583
IT'S NOT HER FAULT.
THAT REPORTER'S AN ASSHOLE.

07:13.583 --> 07:15.333
[ TELEPHONE DIALS ]
SERGEANT?

07:15.333 --> 07:17.583
YEAH, HOLD THE REST OF THEM
DOWNSTAIRS.

07:17.583 --> 07:19.291
WE'RE OUT OF ROOM HERE.

07:19.291 --> 07:20.875
YOU SEEN PASCAL?

07:20.875 --> 07:23.583
YOU KNOW, PASCAL IS JUST CAUGHT
IN A CYCLE OF REACTION.

07:23.583 --> 07:25.917
SHE'S NOT CO-CREATING
HER OWN REALITY.

07:25.917 --> 07:28.709
YOU KNOW THOSE WORDS DON'T
ACTUALLY MEAN ANYTHING, RIGHT?

07:28.709 --> 07:31.583
LOOK AROUND YOU, BRO.
SHE'S MANIFESTING NEGATIVITY.

07:31.583 --> 07:33.625
Masuka:
IT'S ON AGAIN.

07:33.625 --> 07:35.542
EXCUSE ME, LIEUTENANT?
NO COMMENT.

07:35.542 --> 07:37.375
WE HAVE REPORTS THERE
WERE DOZENS OF BODIES FOUND

07:37.375 --> 07:38.792
IN THAT
UNDERWATER GRAVE SITE.

07:38.792 --> 07:40.166
NOT DOZENS.

07:40.166 --> 07:41.792
THE BOSS' SWEATER MELONS
LOOK BIGGER ON TV.

07:41.792 --> 07:44.750
THE OPERATIVE WORD IS "BOSS."
SHOW SOME RESPECT.

07:44.750 --> 07:46.959
I THOUGHT I WAS.

07:46.959 --> 07:49.333
ONE DOZEN?
TWO DOZEN?
18 OR SO.

07:49.333 --> 07:51.792
HAVE THE FAMILIES
BEEN NOTIFIED?

07:51.792 --> 07:53.959
WE'RE STILL TRYING
TO IDENTIFY THEM.

07:53.959 --> 07:56.208
IF VIEWERS HAVE INFORMATION,
THEY SHOULD CONTACT YOU?

07:56.208 --> 07:58.083
YES. FINE.

07:59.667 --> 08:01.250
SO, THERE YOU HAVE IT.

08:01.250 --> 08:04.208
POLICE ARE SEEKING ANY LEADS
THAT CAN HELP THEM IDENTIFY

08:04.208 --> 08:06.917
THE 18 FACELESS VICTIMS
OF THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

08:06.917 --> 08:08.750
IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION,
PLEASE CONTACT...

08:08.750 --> 08:10.875
PASCAL
IS DEFINITELY OFF HER GAME.

08:10.875 --> 08:14.458
WORD IS, HER FIANCÃ© IS CATCHING
SOME STRANGE ON THE SLY.

08:14.458 --> 08:15.917
THAT'D DO IT.

08:15.917 --> 08:18.000
THE SHIT STOPS HERE.
GIVE IT TO ME.

08:18.000 --> 08:21.166
[ TELEVISION CLICKS OFF ]

08:21.166 --> 08:23.792
Dexter: MOST OF THESE PEOPLE
WON'T FIND ANSWERS HERE.

08:23.792 --> 08:25.250
CHANCES ARE GOOD

08:25.250 --> 08:27.208
THEIR LOVED ONES
WEREN'T AMONG MY CHOSEN FEW.

08:28.709 --> 08:31.000
Matthews: MAY I HAVE
YOUR ATTENTION, PLEASE?

08:31.000 --> 08:33.208
FIRST OF ALL,
I WANT TO TELL YOU

08:33.208 --> 08:36.834
WHAT A GREAT JOB YOU'VE ALL BEEN
DOING ON THIS HORRIFIC CASE.

08:36.834 --> 08:39.333
AND WITH THE HELP OF
THE BEST MAN HUNTER IN THE FBI,

08:39.333 --> 08:41.250
WE SHOULD HAVE ANSWERS SOON.

08:41.250 --> 08:43.333
IN THE MEANTIME,
THE DAILY WORK OF THIS PRECINCT

08:43.333 --> 08:45.250
MUST CONTINUE
TO SERVE THE PUBLIC,

08:45.250 --> 08:47.375
SO WE'LL BE DIVIDING UP
OUR RESOURCES.

08:47.375 --> 08:49.917
AGENT LUNDY HAS REQUESTED
THE FOLLOWING OFFICERS

08:49.917 --> 08:51.166
FOR HIS JOINT TASK FORCE.

08:51.166 --> 08:52.834
OFFICER COOK...

08:52.834 --> 08:54.917
LUNDY MADE ME LFI.

08:54.917 --> 08:56.208
LFI?

08:56.208 --> 08:58.500
LEAD FORENSICS INVESTIGATOR.

08:58.500 --> 09:01.041
SORRY YOU GOT BONED,
BUT, HEY, NO BLOOD SPATTER.

09:01.041 --> 09:03.208
[ SIGHS ]
SUCKS TO BE ME.

09:03.208 --> 09:05.750
ACTUALLY, IT KEEPS ME
OFF LUNDY'S RADAR.

09:05.750 --> 09:07.583
SERGEANT LEE.

09:07.583 --> 09:09.834
DETECTIVE RAMOS....

09:12.083 --> 09:14.125
...OFFICER PANKO...

09:14.125 --> 09:15.792
DETECTIVE BATISTA...

09:15.792 --> 09:17.250
YES!

09:17.250 --> 09:19.000
I SAW THIS HAPPENING.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.583
...AND OFFICER DEBRA MORGAN.

09:23.125 --> 09:26.417
THOSE CALLED WILL REPORT
DIRECTLY TO SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY.

09:26.417 --> 09:29.500
AND LET'S NOT FORGET
THIS IS ON ALL OF US, FOLKS.

09:29.500 --> 09:31.875
LET'S KEEP OUR EYES
AND OUR EARS OPEN.

09:31.875 --> 09:35.583
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER WAS
AN AMATEUR COMPARED TO THIS GUY.

09:38.083 --> 09:39.417
Lundy:
I'D ALSO APPRECIATE IT

09:39.417 --> 09:41.333
IF YOUR LIEUTENANT
WOULD CONSULT WITH ME

09:41.333 --> 09:42.542
BEFORE SPEAKING
TO THE PRESS.

09:42.542 --> 09:45.125
I'LL RIP HER A NEW ONE...
IF I CAN FIND HER.

09:47.500 --> 09:50.959
PRINTS, FIBER,
TRACE EVIDENCE --

09:50.959 --> 09:53.375
NO, THEY WON'T FIND ANYTHING.

09:53.375 --> 09:55.166
I FOLLOWED
ALL OF HARRY'S

09:55.166 --> 09:57.667
PAINSTAKING
PREVENTATIVE MEASURES.

09:57.667 --> 09:59.750
HE KNEW THAT NOTHING
STAYS BURIED FOREVER.

09:59.750 --> 10:01.792
HIS CODE WILL PROTECT ME.

10:01.792 --> 10:04.709
STILL, I WISH MY OWN SISTER
WEREN'T HUNTING ME --

10:04.709 --> 10:08.333
MAKES FOR
AN AWKWARD FAMILY DYNAMIC.

10:08.333 --> 10:12.208
Lundy: SO, I'M A FED.
MY SUIT PROVES IT.

10:12.208 --> 10:14.625
THE OTHER SUITS HERE ARE FEDS.

10:14.625 --> 10:19.041
BUT SUIT OR...
UGLY HAWAIIAN SHIRT --

10:19.041 --> 10:21.542
NO OFFENSE --

10:21.542 --> 10:22.834
WE'RE A TEAM.

10:22.834 --> 10:25.375
AND OUR FIRST PLAY
IS I.D.ing THOSE BODIES.

10:25.375 --> 10:27.125
ONCE WE KNOW WHO THEY ARE,

10:27.125 --> 10:29.792
WE'LL FILL IN EVERY DETAIL
OF THEIR LIVES,

10:29.792 --> 10:33.000
FROM THEIR HUEVOS RANCHOS
TO THEIR CRÃ¨ME BRÃ»LÃ©E.

10:33.000 --> 10:36.417
AND, UH,
GET USED TO FOOD REFERENCES

10:36.417 --> 10:39.625
'CAUSE, WELL, I LIKE FOOD.

10:39.625 --> 10:41.458
VINCE MASUKA AND HIS TEAM

10:41.458 --> 10:43.709
ARE GATHERING DNA, PRINTS,
AND DENTAL RECORDS.

10:43.709 --> 10:47.083
THE REST OF US ARE GOING
TO CULL THROUGH COLD CASES
AND MISSING-PERSONS FILES.

10:47.083 --> 10:49.917
ALSO, I WANT THAT CROWD
OUT THERE INTERVIEWED --

10:49.917 --> 10:52.417
THOUGH MOST OF THEM
WILL BE A WASTE OF TIME.

10:52.417 --> 10:54.125
NEGATIVE THINKING.

10:54.125 --> 10:57.083
YOU FOUR, MOVE THEM OUT
AS QUICKLY AS YOU CAN,

10:57.083 --> 10:58.625
BUT BE THOROUGH.

10:58.625 --> 11:01.500
IF WE GET EVEN ONE HIT,
IT'LL BE WORTH IT.

11:01.500 --> 11:03.667
EVERYONE ELSE, WORK THE FILES.

11:03.667 --> 11:07.291
REMEMBER,
I.D.s WILL LEAD TO A PATTERN,

11:07.291 --> 11:09.667
WHICH WILL LEAD TO OUR MAN.

11:12.250 --> 11:18.083
WHEN THE MANHUNT IS ON,
THE HUNTED GO SHOPPING.

11:18.083 --> 11:20.000
NOT FOR A NEW CAR --

11:20.000 --> 11:21.750
FOR MY NEXT PROJECT.

11:21.750 --> 11:23.834
I WON'T ACT ON IT...YET.

11:23.834 --> 11:27.667
I'M STILL LAYING LOW.
HARRY WOULD INSIST ON THAT.

11:27.667 --> 11:30.625
JUST GETTING THE RESEARCH
OUT OF THE WAY.

11:30.625 --> 11:34.083
SOMEONE TALKED HIS WAY
INTO THE HOMES OF TWO WOMEN

11:34.083 --> 11:36.250
AND DIDN'T LEAVE
TILL THEY WERE DEAD.

11:36.250 --> 11:40.125
ANN COHEN AND,
A MONTH BEFORE HER, LYNN HALL.

11:40.125 --> 11:42.083
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

11:42.083 --> 11:45.500
A CERTAIN CAR DEALERSHIP RAN
CREDIT CHECKS ON BOTH WOMEN.

11:45.500 --> 11:47.041
BOTH BOUGHT CARS ELSEWHERE,

11:47.041 --> 11:50.333
SO NOBODY
THOUGHT ABOUT IT TWICE.

11:50.333 --> 11:53.500
BUT WHO REQUESTED
THOSE CREDIT CHECKS?

11:55.125 --> 11:57.000
ROGER HICKS.

11:58.250 --> 12:00.208
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

12:00.208 --> 12:02.583
ALL I NEED
IS SOME DNA PROOF --

12:02.583 --> 12:05.041
CUP OF COFFEE
SHOULD DO THE TRICK.

12:15.000 --> 12:17.166
HOW MANY KIDS YOU GOT?

12:18.375 --> 12:20.542
[ LAUGHS ]
ENOUGH.

12:20.542 --> 12:23.000
[ CHUCKLES ]
I HEAR YOU.

12:23.000 --> 12:26.917
WHEN MY TWO CAME ALONG,
IT WAS BYE-BYE, CONVERTIBLE.

12:26.917 --> 12:29.917
OF COURSE...
THEY'RE WORTH IT.

12:29.917 --> 12:32.083
MUST TAKE AFTER THEIR MOM.

12:32.083 --> 12:35.583
THAT THEY DO.
THANK GOD.

12:35.583 --> 12:37.417
I TELL YOU,
I MISS MY CONVERTIBLE,

12:37.417 --> 12:40.250
BUT, UH, TRUTH --

12:40.250 --> 12:42.291
MY MINIVAN'S
GOT A MUCH NICER RIDE.

12:42.291 --> 12:43.417
SO YOU OWN ONE.

12:43.417 --> 12:44.709
OH, THE SAME ONE
YOU'RE LOOKING AT.

12:44.709 --> 12:46.750
I MEAN, I KNOW --
WHIPPED, RIGHT?

12:46.750 --> 12:49.875
BUT, UH, MY KIDS
LOVE THE TWIN DVDs.

12:49.875 --> 12:52.041
THEY'RE JUST CRAZY ABOUT
SPONGEBOB, YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

12:52.041 --> 12:53.250
ACTUALLY, I DO.

12:53.250 --> 12:57.417
MY WIFE LOVES THE NAV SYSTEM
AND ALL THE SAFETY FEATURES.

12:57.417 --> 12:59.709
AND WHEN THEY'RE HAPPY...

12:59.709 --> 13:01.083
YOU'RE HAPPY.
THAT'S RIGHT.

13:01.083 --> 13:03.875
EXCEPT THE KIDS DON'T EXIST,
NEITHER DOES THE WIFE.

13:03.875 --> 13:06.500
AND HE OWNS A BEEMER,
NOT A MINIVAN.

13:06.500 --> 13:08.959
STILL, HE'S SEAMLESS.

13:08.959 --> 13:09.834
IMPRESSIVE.

13:09.834 --> 13:12.291
IT'S NOT FLASHY, BUT...

13:12.291 --> 13:13.375
WHAT DID FLASH EVER GET ME?

13:13.375 --> 13:14.750
IT GOT ME PULLED OVER,
THAT'S WHAT.

13:14.750 --> 13:16.625
I'M DEFINITELY
NOT INTO FLASH.

13:16.625 --> 13:19.333
YOU GOT TO SIT
IN THE CAPTAIN'S CHAIR, THOUGH.

13:19.333 --> 13:20.792
IT'S LIKE A 747, MAN.

13:20.792 --> 13:22.333
MANUEL, HOLD UP.

13:24.041 --> 13:25.458
THANK YOU, SIR.

13:25.458 --> 13:27.041
SO, UH...

13:27.041 --> 13:29.792
WE SHOULD TAKE IT OUT.
CHECK OUT THE RIDE.

13:29.792 --> 13:30.834
I'M JUST DOING RESEARCH.

13:30.834 --> 13:32.959
OKAY, YOU DON'T WANT
A BIG SALES PITCH.

13:32.959 --> 13:34.000
I GET THAT.

13:34.000 --> 13:37.083
LET ME AT LEAST
PULL THE SPECS FOR YOU.

13:37.083 --> 13:38.750
BECAUSE, TRUTHFULLY,

13:38.750 --> 13:40.792
WE HAVE A HARD TIME
KEEPING THESE ON THE LOT.

13:40.792 --> 13:42.333
YOU MIGHT WANT TO GRAB
THE TEST-DRIVE

13:42.333 --> 13:43.667
WHILE IT'S STILL HERE.

13:43.667 --> 13:45.834
I THINK I HAVE
ALL THE INFORMATION I NEED

13:45.834 --> 13:47.083
TO MAKE A DECISION.

13:47.083 --> 13:47.917
YEAH?

13:47.917 --> 13:49.458
WELL, THEN,
YOU'VE SEEN THE, UH,

13:49.458 --> 13:50.834
THE STOW 'N GO
SEATING SYSTEM, RIGHT?

13:52.000 --> 13:56.542
I HAVE HAD
EVERYTHING IN HERE

13:56.542 --> 13:59.792
FROM A SOCCER TEAM
TO A FREAKIN' DEER CARCASS.

13:59.792 --> 14:02.583
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT,
OF COURSE.

14:02.583 --> 14:06.333
BUT, UH, I SURE WAS GLAD
FOR THE AMPLE CARGO SPACE,

14:06.333 --> 14:07.834
NOT TO MENTION
THE TINTED WINDOWS.

14:09.750 --> 14:12.166
I CAN SEE
HOW THAT MIGHT COME IN HANDY.

14:12.166 --> 14:14.959
I'LL JUST GRAB THE KEYS.

14:29.792 --> 14:32.333
I GO TO STALK A KILLER
AND I END UP WITH A NEW CAR?

14:32.333 --> 14:33.417
HOW'D THAT HAPPEN?

14:33.417 --> 14:35.458
NEW CAR?

14:35.458 --> 14:37.583
YEAH.

14:37.583 --> 14:40.041
YOU GET MARRIED?

14:40.041 --> 14:41.709
NOT THAT I KNOW OF.

14:41.709 --> 14:43.959
HUH.

14:43.959 --> 14:47.375
SO WHAT'S WITH
THE MOMMY MOBILE?

14:47.375 --> 14:48.875
I'M, UH...

14:48.875 --> 14:51.500
NOT SURE.

15:02.834 --> 15:04.667
SYNTHETIC.

15:04.667 --> 15:06.750
EVEN ROGER'S HAIR IS A LIE.

15:06.750 --> 15:09.000
I COULD LEARN A THING OR TWO
FROM THIS GUY.

15:09.000 --> 15:10.208
[ DOOR OPENS ]

15:10.208 --> 15:12.458
WHO'S YOUR DADDY?

15:12.458 --> 15:14.875
UH...HARRY MORGAN.

15:14.875 --> 15:17.625
DUDE, THE LEAD
FORENSICS INVESTIGATOR

15:17.625 --> 15:20.375
OF THE JOINT TASK FORCE --
THAT'S WHO.

15:20.375 --> 15:22.542
OH, OKAY.

15:22.542 --> 15:24.750
SO, YOU WANT IN
ON THIS BITCH OR NOT?

15:24.750 --> 15:25.917
WHAT BITCH?

15:25.917 --> 15:28.834
THE ONLY BITCH IN TOWN, BABY.
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

15:28.834 --> 15:31.750
I GOT YOU
TEMPORARILY ASSIGNED.

15:31.750 --> 15:33.417
VINCE, YOU DIDN'T
HAVE TO DO THAT.

15:33.417 --> 15:34.583
NOTHING SEXY, OF COURSE,

15:34.583 --> 15:36.667
JUST SOME BONE-MARROW
COLLECTION FOR DNA I.D.s.

15:36.667 --> 15:38.000
BUT IT'LL GET YOU
IN THE TENT.

15:38.000 --> 15:39.333
AND YOU GOT TO SEE
THE TENT.

15:39.333 --> 15:40.250
AMAZING.

15:43.709 --> 15:44.875
SAY IT.

15:44.875 --> 15:46.208
[ SIGHS ]

15:46.208 --> 15:47.333
YOU'RE MY DADDY.

15:47.333 --> 15:49.083
IT SOUNDS WEIRD
WHEN YOU SAY IT.

15:49.083 --> 15:53.041
I HAVEN'T BEEN MUCH USE
SINCE HE DISAPPEARED.

15:53.041 --> 15:56.917
I KNOW I'M SUPPOSED TO
MOVE ON,

15:56.917 --> 15:58.375
BUT...

15:58.375 --> 16:01.792
HERE'S THE PICTURE OF HIM.

16:01.792 --> 16:03.625
HE LOOKS...

16:05.083 --> 16:06.000
...NICE.

16:07.792 --> 16:11.750
NOT ACCORDING TO MY MOTHER...
OR THE POLICE.

16:11.750 --> 16:14.291
HE WAS IN AND OUT OF JAIL,

16:14.291 --> 16:18.500
BUT MY HEART RACED
WHENEVER I SAW HIM.

16:19.875 --> 16:22.291
I BROUGHT HIS TOOTHBRUSH.

16:22.291 --> 16:24.333
THEY SAY
YOU CAN GET DNA OFF IT.

16:24.333 --> 16:28.917
YOU CAN FIND HIM
WITH THIS, RIGHT?

16:38.250 --> 16:41.291
SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY?

16:41.291 --> 16:44.667
LOOK, THANKS FOR CHOOSING ME
FOR THE TASK FORCE AND ALL,

16:44.667 --> 16:47.542
BUT I'D APPRECIATE
YOU FINDING SOMEONE ELSE.

16:47.542 --> 16:48.959
YOU WANT OFF?

16:48.959 --> 16:52.000
JUST AS SOON AS
YOU CAN REPLACE ME, SIR.

16:52.000 --> 16:54.583
THIS IS A CHANCE TO SOLVE
A PRETTY IMPORTANT CASE.

16:54.583 --> 16:57.458
MOST PEOPLE GET INTO THIS
LINE OF WORK TO DO JUST THAT.

16:58.458 --> 17:02.000
WELL, I'VE GOT
CASES OF MY OWN BACKING UP,

17:02.000 --> 17:04.667
AND THE PRECINCT'S SHORTHANDED
WITH ALL THIS SHIT.

17:04.667 --> 17:07.125
SO, IF YOU DON'T MIND...

17:08.041 --> 17:09.792
I'LL SEE WHAT I CAN DO.

17:09.792 --> 17:13.750
IN THE MEANTIME, IF YOU COULD
CONTINUE THE INTERVIEWS...

17:13.750 --> 17:16.208
YEAH.
YEAH, OF COURSE.

17:16.208 --> 17:18.125
THANK YOU.

17:25.041 --> 17:27.208
MOST OF 'EM HAVE
BEEN UNDERWATER FOR YEARS.

17:27.208 --> 17:29.750
BUT SOME, IT'S AWESOME,
YOU CAN'T EVEN TELL.

17:29.750 --> 17:31.125
THE TEMPERATURE
ON THE OCEAN FLOOR

17:31.125 --> 17:33.291
AND THE AIRTIGHT BAGS
KEPT THEM INTACT.

17:33.291 --> 17:35.875
I MEAN, A LITTLE GELATINOUS
RESIDUE, SURE. BUT...

17:35.875 --> 17:38.208
I'D RATHER REMEMBER MY
OLD PLAYMATES AS THEY WERE --

17:38.208 --> 17:40.125
NEAT, CLEAN LITTLE PACKAGES.

17:40.125 --> 17:42.291
YOU KNOW, VINCE, I APPRECIATE
YOU DOING ME THIS FAVOR BUT --

17:42.291 --> 17:44.458
ACTUALLY, YOU'RE
DOING ME THE FAVOR.

17:44.458 --> 17:45.375
I NEED YOUR HELP, BUDDY.

17:45.375 --> 17:47.709
THE PRESSURE'S
FUCKING RIDONKULOUS.

17:47.709 --> 17:50.291
GLAD TO BE OF SERVICE.

17:50.291 --> 17:52.625
FIELD MORGUE
FOR THE OVERFLOW,

17:52.625 --> 17:53.875
BUT IT'S
STATE-OF-THE-ART.

17:53.875 --> 17:56.208
FUCKING FBI, EH?

17:56.208 --> 17:59.041
[ MACHINERY WHIRRING ]

18:03.208 --> 18:05.875
A GOOD PERCENTAGE
ARE JUST BONES.

18:05.875 --> 18:07.417
MUST HAVE FED THE FISH
WHEN THE BAGS TORE.

18:07.417 --> 18:09.583
HUMPTY FUCKING DUMPTY,
RIGHT?

18:09.583 --> 18:11.250
EXACTLY.

18:11.250 --> 18:14.375
THEY WEREN'T
MEANT TO BE PUT TOGETHER AGAIN.

18:14.375 --> 18:16.625
THEY WERE MEANT TO REMAIN
IN THE SILENT SHADOWS,

18:16.625 --> 18:19.959
KEEPING THEIR SECRETS.

18:19.959 --> 18:22.083
NOW THEY'RE
EXPOSED TO THE GLARE,

18:22.083 --> 18:27.417
REFLECTING MY DARKNESS LIKE
SOME GROTESQUE CARNIVAL MIRROR.

18:27.417 --> 18:31.333
HARRY WAS RIGHT --
NOTHING STAYS BURIED.

18:31.333 --> 18:33.709
PERHAPS NOT EVEN ME.

18:40.667 --> 18:43.625
LOOKING FOR MY TAURUS,
SERGEANT?

18:43.625 --> 18:45.250
KEEP LOOKING.

18:45.250 --> 18:48.125
YOU DON'T NEED TO KNOW
WHERE I'M GOING TONIGHT.

18:48.125 --> 18:50.583
AND GENIUS ME,

18:50.583 --> 18:53.542
NOT ONLY DO I LEAVE
MY WORKS IN MY GIRLFRIEND'S CAR,

18:53.542 --> 18:57.083
BUT ALSO ALL THE DEAD FISH
FROM THE FISHING TRIP, RIGHT?

18:57.083 --> 18:58.375
[ LIGHT LAUGHTER ]

18:58.375 --> 19:01.750
THEN I COLLAPSE
IN HER PARENTS' HOUSE,

19:01.750 --> 19:03.834
SCARE HER KIDS,

19:03.834 --> 19:06.000
AND  GET MYSELF FIRED,
'CAUSE GUESS WHAT --

19:06.000 --> 19:06.959
WE WORK TOGETHER.

19:06.959 --> 19:08.583
Man: AW.

19:08.583 --> 19:09.792
YEAH.

19:10.834 --> 19:14.583
SO, NOW, WELL,

19:14.583 --> 19:16.458
I'M 20-DAYS SOBER...

19:16.458 --> 19:19.125
AGAIN...

19:19.125 --> 19:21.291
HOPING TO MAKE IT TO 21.

19:26.250 --> 19:28.542
THANKS, GORDON.

19:28.542 --> 19:33.834
THIS MEETING RECOGNIZES
LENGTHS OF SOBRIETY WITH CHIPS.

19:33.834 --> 19:39.208
SO, IF THERE'S ANYONE WHO
WOULD LIKE A NEWCOMER'S CHIP...

19:42.000 --> 19:43.959
[ APPLAUSE ]

19:48.208 --> 19:51.333
YOU'VE GOT THREE MINUTES
TO SHARE IF YOU WANT IT.

19:51.333 --> 19:53.792
OH, REALLY?

19:53.792 --> 19:55.458
GO AHEAD, MAN.
YOU AMONG FRIENDS.

20:03.000 --> 20:06.917
WELL, I, UH...

20:06.917 --> 20:09.583
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

20:09.583 --> 20:11.500
[ British accent ]
WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

20:14.750 --> 20:16.291
BOB.

20:16.291 --> 20:17.625
All: HI, BOB.

20:17.625 --> 20:19.166
HI.

20:19.166 --> 20:23.208
AND I'M, UM...

20:23.208 --> 20:24.208
AN ADDICT.

20:24.208 --> 20:28.709
I USE...HEROIN --

20:28.709 --> 20:30.917
SHOOT IT.

20:30.917 --> 20:32.208
IT'S AFFECTING MY JOB.

20:32.208 --> 20:35.250
MY BOSS FOUND MY WORKS.
HE FIRED MY ASS.

20:35.250 --> 20:36.500
BUT I SHOWED HIM --

20:36.500 --> 20:39.083
I SPENT EVERY PENNY
OF MY FINAL PAYCHECK ON JUNK.

20:39.083 --> 20:40.542
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:40.542 --> 20:43.250
DOCTOR SAID I...

20:47.542 --> 20:49.250
...UH...

20:52.000 --> 20:54.542
...I ALMOST DIED.

21:02.083 --> 21:03.917
COFFEE SUCKS...

21:03.917 --> 21:06.166
AS BAD
AS THE DOUGHNUTS.

21:06.166 --> 21:07.709
IT'S BETTER NEXT DOOR.

21:07.709 --> 21:08.625
COME ON.

21:16.750 --> 21:18.125
MMM.

21:18.125 --> 21:21.625
IT IS GOOD COFFEE.
THANK YOU.

21:23.917 --> 21:25.250
SO, TELL ME...

21:25.250 --> 21:26.792
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

21:26.792 --> 21:30.250
EXACTLY HOW FULL OF SHIT
ARE YOU?

21:32.458 --> 21:36.041
I'M NOT FULL OF ANYTHING.

21:36.041 --> 21:39.083
IT WAS A NICE PERFORMANCE
IN THERE.

21:39.083 --> 21:42.417
WHERE DID YOU DOWNLOAD IT FROM?
Addict.com?

21:44.000 --> 21:47.500
LOOK,
I HAVE NO REASON TO LIE.

21:47.500 --> 21:49.125
SURE YOU DO.

21:49.125 --> 21:51.458
WE ALL DO.

21:51.458 --> 21:53.375
YOU THOUGHT I WAS LYING?

21:53.375 --> 21:56.208
I DON'T KNOW...
BOB.

21:56.208 --> 21:59.834
[ CHUCKLES ]
WELL, IT IS ANONYMOUS.

21:59.834 --> 22:01.667
EVERYONE IN THAT ROOM

22:01.667 --> 22:06.000
HAS HEARD OR LIVED FAR WORSE
THAN ANYTHING YOU'VE EVER DONE.

22:07.625 --> 22:09.166
I DOUBT IT.

22:09.166 --> 22:12.417
OH, SO YOU'RE
SUPER-JUNKIE.

22:12.417 --> 22:14.583
I DON'T MEAN TO IMPLY

22:14.583 --> 22:17.000
THAT WHAT YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH
HASN'T BEEN DIFFICULT.

22:17.000 --> 22:18.750
BUT THERE'S NO WAY

22:18.750 --> 22:21.792
THAT I COULD KNOW WHAT
YOU'VE EXPERIENCED, RIGHT?

22:24.792 --> 22:29.542
I COULDN'T
POSSIBLY FEEL THAT NEED.

22:31.500 --> 22:37.083
LIKE A THOUSAND HIDING VOICES
WHISPERING,

22:37.083 --> 22:39.542
"This is who you are."

22:42.166 --> 22:44.917
AND YOU FIGHT THE PRESSURE,

22:44.917 --> 22:49.333
THE GROWING NEED
RISING LIKE A WAVE,

22:49.333 --> 22:55.959
PRICKLING AND TEASING
AND PRODDING TO BE FED.

22:55.959 --> 22:58.959
BUT THE WHISPERING
GETS LOUDER

22:58.959 --> 23:01.542
UNTIL IT'S SCREAMING, "NOW!"

23:03.709 --> 23:07.417
AND IT'S THE ONLY VOICE
YOU HEAR...

23:09.583 --> 23:12.667
THE ONLY VOICE
YOU WANT  TO HEAR.

23:15.083 --> 23:17.750
AND YOU BELONG TO IT,

23:17.750 --> 23:20.750
TO THIS...

23:20.750 --> 23:23.917
SHADOW SELF.

23:25.667 --> 23:26.917
TO THIS...

23:30.125 --> 23:33.375
DARK PASSENGER.

23:33.375 --> 23:35.333
YES.

23:37.709 --> 23:40.083
THE DARK PASSENGER.

23:45.834 --> 23:46.959
NO.

23:48.208 --> 23:50.333
[ SIGHS ]

23:50.333 --> 23:53.792
I'M SORRY,
BUT I NEED TO GO.

23:53.792 --> 23:55.083
[ CHUCKLES ]

23:55.083 --> 23:57.208
THANKS FOR THE COFFEE.

24:02.917 --> 24:04.709
SHE KNOWS.

24:06.875 --> 24:09.625
SHE RECOGNIZES DEMONS...

24:09.625 --> 24:12.083
DARK PASSENGERS.

24:12.083 --> 24:13.917
MAYBE THE OTHERS CAN, TOO.

24:13.917 --> 24:17.250
THIS PROGRAM IS TOO RISKY,
ESPECIALLY NOW.

24:17.250 --> 24:19.417
RITA WILL HAVE TO UNDERSTAND.

24:32.583 --> 24:35.458
[ KEYS JINGLE, DOOR UNLOCKS ]

24:39.500 --> 24:42.750
HEY.
YOU JUST MISSED STORY TIME.

24:42.750 --> 24:44.792
I WAS AT A MEETING.

24:44.792 --> 24:47.792
[ SIGHS ]

24:47.792 --> 24:49.583
THANK YOU.

24:51.625 --> 24:54.333
IT MADE ME REALIZE
SOMETHING IMPORTANT.

24:54.333 --> 24:56.417
OH, REALLY?
WHAT'S THAT?

24:56.417 --> 24:59.750
THOSE MEETINGS ARE
NOT A GOOD PLACE FOR ME.

25:02.583 --> 25:06.250
I KNOW HOW THIS SOUNDS,
BUT I CAN DO THIS ON MY OWN.

25:06.250 --> 25:07.875
DEXTER, YOU NEED A PROGRAM.

25:07.875 --> 25:10.208
I'VE READ STUDIES --
PEOPLE ARE 10 TIMES AS LIKELY

25:10.208 --> 25:11.375
TO CHANGE ON THEIR OWN

25:11.375 --> 25:13.458
AS THEY ARE WITH THE HELP
OF DOCTORS OR PROGRAMS.

25:13.458 --> 25:15.834
SO YOU'RE QUOTING STUDIES?

25:15.834 --> 25:17.834
LOOK, I LIVED THIS.

25:17.834 --> 25:20.917
I WATCHED PAUL TRY AND FAIL
WITH WHITE-KNUCKLE SOBRIETY.

25:20.917 --> 25:23.792
I'M NOT PAUL.
I'M NOT ANY OF THOSE PEOPLE.

25:23.792 --> 25:26.166
GOING TO THOSE MEETINGS
WILL DO MORE HARM THAN GOOD,

25:26.166 --> 25:27.333
I SWEAR TO YOU.

25:27.333 --> 25:28.709
I'M BETTER OFF ALONE.

25:36.333 --> 25:38.625
I PRAY YOU CHANGE YOUR MIND.

25:44.166 --> 25:47.041
WHAT JUST HAPPENED?

25:47.041 --> 25:50.291
[ INDISTINCT TALKING
ON TELEVISION ]

25:50.291 --> 25:53.083
[ DOOR OPENS, CHAIN CLINKS ]

25:53.083 --> 25:54.667
DEB?

25:54.667 --> 25:56.875
[ SIGHS ]
DEB?

26:06.542 --> 26:09.083
THOUGHT YOU WERE STAYING
AT RITA'S.

26:09.083 --> 26:11.250
UH...

26:11.250 --> 26:13.583
TAKING THE NIGHT OFF.

26:16.709 --> 26:20.500
I THOUGHT YOU'D BE
ON THE TREADMILL.

26:20.500 --> 26:22.291
TAKING THE NIGHT OFF.

26:22.291 --> 26:24.875
WITH NO MONEY DOWN, GUARANTEED,

26:24.875 --> 26:27.083
OR WE'LL MAKE
YOUR FIRST TWO PAYMENTS...

26:27.083 --> 26:31.625
Dexter: A NIGHT OFF IS GOOD
TO REMEMBER WHAT'S IMPORTANT.

26:42.417 --> 26:44.250
TWO WOMEN ARE DEAD,

26:44.250 --> 26:45.875
THE KILLER IS SELLING MINIVANS,

26:45.875 --> 26:47.709
AND I HAVE AN OPPORTUNITY
TO PROVE IT,

26:47.709 --> 26:49.500
EVEN IF I AM LAYING LOW.

26:49.500 --> 26:51.500
HAVING A VICTIM
PREPPED AND READY

26:51.500 --> 26:53.208
WILL TAKE THE EDGE
OFF THE WAIT...

26:53.208 --> 26:54.375
I HOPE.

26:54.375 --> 26:56.375
HEY, HANG ON
JUST A SECOND, OKAY?

26:56.375 --> 26:58.625
WHAT'S GOING ON,
DEX?
HEY.

26:58.625 --> 27:01.166
ANY PROBLEMS, THE SERVICE CENTER
CAN TAKE CARE OF YOU,

27:01.166 --> 27:03.125
BUT THEY'RE
AROUND THE CORNER.

27:03.125 --> 27:04.834
ACTUALLY,
THE MINIVAN'S FINE.

27:04.834 --> 27:07.083
WELL, OF COURSE IT IS.
I NEVER SOLD A LEMON IN MY LIFE.

27:07.083 --> 27:08.834
I'M JUST RETHINKING
THE EXTENDED WARRANTY.

27:08.834 --> 27:10.917
GREAT, I'LL SET YOU UP
WITH A WARRANTY WRITER, THEN.

27:10.917 --> 27:13.125
AND I'M THINKING ROOF RACK
AND PREMIUM SOUND SYSTEM.

27:13.125 --> 27:14.625
GOING ALL OUT.
YEAH.

27:14.625 --> 27:16.500
THAT'S GREAT,
BUT I'M WITH A CUSTOMER.

27:16.500 --> 27:18.125
AND SO
ONE OF MY ASSOCIATES --

27:18.125 --> 27:19.417
I'D RATHER DEAL WITH YOU.

27:19.417 --> 27:21.125
I'LL JUST WAIT FOR YOU
IN YOUR OFFICE.

27:21.125 --> 27:22.625
OUTSTANDING.

27:32.458 --> 27:35.750
DNA, DNA, COME OUT AND PLAY.

27:39.709 --> 27:42.625
UH-OH, ROGER'S GOT YOU
IN THE BOX.

27:42.625 --> 27:45.500
ONCE YOU'RE IN THE BOX, YOU
DON'T LEAVE WITHOUT A DEAL.

27:45.500 --> 27:47.291
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]
UH-OH.

27:47.291 --> 27:49.208
DON'T WORRY.
YOU'RE SAFE WITH ROGER.

27:49.208 --> 27:50.208
HE'S THE BEST.

27:50.208 --> 27:53.291
I'M JUST DROPPING OFF
THIS THANK-YOU NOTE.

27:53.291 --> 27:55.458
WELL, I WAS JUST LEAVING.

27:55.458 --> 27:58.166
HE SENT YOU ACROSS THE STREET,
DIDN'T HE?

27:58.166 --> 27:59.834
ACROSS THE STREET?

27:59.834 --> 28:01.583
IT'S OKAY, HE TOLD ME
NOT TO TELL ANYONE EITHER.

28:01.583 --> 28:03.542
YEAH, I DON'T KNOW
HOW HE MAKES A LIVING

28:03.542 --> 28:06.500
SENDING ALL OF HIS COMMISSIONS
TO OTHER DEALERS.

28:06.500 --> 28:08.166
MAYBE HE HAS
ULTERIOR MOTIVES.

28:08.166 --> 28:11.000
OR MAYBE HE KNOWS
I CAN'T AFFORD HIS PRICE.

28:11.000 --> 28:13.083
AFTER HE RAN A CREDIT CHECK?

28:13.083 --> 28:15.125
TRW DOESN'T LIE.

28:15.125 --> 28:16.792
SO, YOU'RE SINGLE?

28:18.583 --> 28:19.917
Y-YEAH.

28:19.917 --> 28:21.041
MAKES IT TOUGHER TO AFFORD

28:21.041 --> 28:23.542
THOSE BIG-TICKET ITEMS,
LIKE CARS AND HOUSES.

28:23.542 --> 28:25.000
YOU RENT AN APARTMENT?

28:25.000 --> 28:27.750
A HOUSE. I HATE SHARING WALLS.
YOU CAN HEAR EVERYTHING.

28:27.750 --> 28:30.250
TELL ME ABOUT IT.
NO PETS, THOUGH, RIGHT?

28:30.250 --> 28:31.834
Yeah.

28:31.834 --> 28:35.000
IS THIS A COME-ON?
'CAUSE IT'S A LITTLE WEIRD.

28:35.000 --> 28:38.041
IT MUST BE
WHY I'M STILL SINGLE.

28:38.041 --> 28:39.917
ANOTHER BRUNETTE.

28:41.041 --> 28:46.291
SINGLE, NEIGHBORS
AT A DISTANCE, NO GUARD DOG.

28:46.291 --> 28:50.917
THE CREDIT CHECK GETS ROGER
ALL THE DETAILS HE NEEDS.

28:50.917 --> 28:55.500
SHE'S NEXT, AND I CAN'T DO
ANYTHING ABOUT IT --

28:55.500 --> 28:58.041
NOT UNTIL THIS MANHUNT ENDS.

28:58.041 --> 28:59.834
HARRY WOULD INSIST ON IT.

29:07.125 --> 29:10.959
WHAT?
NO, I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.

29:10.959 --> 29:12.583
I KNOW THE CARD IS IN HIS NAME.

29:12.583 --> 29:15.792
I JUST WANT TO CHECK
THE CHARGES.

29:15.792 --> 29:18.917
WELL, THE SUPERVISOR I SPOKE
WITH THIS MORNING ALLOWED IT.

29:18.917 --> 29:22.417
YES -- NO, UH...
YEAH, I'LL HOLD.

29:22.417 --> 29:24.375
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]
YES?

29:24.375 --> 29:26.542
JUST A REMINDER

29:26.542 --> 29:29.125
THAT THE BISCAYNE DRIVE-BY
WARRANT NEEDS YOUR APPROVAL.

29:29.125 --> 29:30.583
I'LL LOOK AT IT.

29:30.583 --> 29:32.417
AND THE HOMICIDE
THAT CAME IN LAST NIGHT

29:32.417 --> 29:34.333
STILL NEEDS TO BE ASSIGNED.

29:34.333 --> 29:35.250
RIGHT, THANKS.

29:35.250 --> 29:38.583
[ SIGHS ]

29:38.583 --> 29:41.875
LOOK, ESMEE,
I KNOW THAT THINGS ARE ROUGH

29:41.875 --> 29:44.834
WITH YOU AND YOUR FIANCÃ© RIGHT
NOW, AND I'M SORRY, REALLY,

29:44.834 --> 29:46.834
BUT WE NEED TO KEEP CLEARING
THAT BOARD OUT THERE.

29:46.834 --> 29:49.417
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
I'M SORRY.

29:49.417 --> 29:51.291
[ SCOFFS ]

29:51.291 --> 29:53.125
I SEEM TO HAVE HAD MY HEAD
UP MY ASS LATELY.

29:53.125 --> 29:55.959
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S CALLED "BEING HUMAN."

