WHAT'S TAKING SO LONG?

33:00.333 --> 33:03.375
EVERY COP ON THE DAMN FORCE
WANTS IN ON THIS CASE.

33:03.375 --> 33:05.959
JUST TAKE YOUR PICK.

33:05.959 --> 33:08.875
I'VE BEEN WONDERING
ABOUT THAT, ACTUALLY.

33:08.875 --> 33:13.333
EVERYONE WANTS ON,
BUT YOU WANT OFF.

33:13.333 --> 33:16.458
I TOLD YOU, I HAVE CASES.

33:16.458 --> 33:18.000
I DON'T THINK SO.

33:18.000 --> 33:20.208
You don't think so.

33:20.208 --> 33:24.375
JESUS, I JUST DON'T WANT TO BE
ON YOUR TASK FORCE, ALL RIGHT?

33:24.375 --> 33:25.667
WHY?

33:25.667 --> 33:28.834
BECAUSE I'M THE LAST PERSON IN
THE WORLD THAT SHOULD BE ON IT.

33:28.834 --> 33:31.458
YOU WANT ME
