YOU WENT THROUGH.

33:41.542 --> 33:44.000
YOU SURVIVED.

33:44.000 --> 33:46.041
I DON'T KNOW HOW.

33:46.041 --> 33:48.667
I CAN'T BEGIN TO IMAGINE
THE STRENGTH IT TOOK --

33:48.667 --> 33:50.959
CONTINUES TO TAKE.

33:50.959 --> 33:54.542
MORE THAN THAT,
YOU GOT A FIRSTHAND LOOK

33:54.542 --> 33:57.083
INTO THE MIND AND HEART
OF A KILLER,

33:57.083 --> 34:00.667
AND YOU'RE STILL HERE.

34:00.667 --> 34:05.166
IF YOU CAN ACCEPT THAT --
REALLY ACCEPT IT --

34:05.166 --> 34:08.125
YOU COULD USE IT.

34:08.125 --> 34:11.166
MIX THAT WITH SOME
OF YOUR STRENGTH, AND...

34:11.166 --> 34:13.041
YOU COULD CATCH SOMEONE
EVEN WORSE

34:13.041 --> 34:14.417
THAN THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

34:18.208 --> 34:20.417
BUT YOU HAVE TO STOP RUNNING.

34:24.417 --> 34:27.959
FINISH TODAY'S INTERVIEWS.

34:27.959 --> 34:31.542
THEN, IF YOU STILL WANT OUT,
YOU GOT IT.

34:37.625 --> 34:40.208
LEAD FUCKING INVESTIGATOR.

34:40.208 --> 34:42.291
TRANSLATION --
EVERYONE'S BITCH.

34:42.291 --> 34:44.500
I DO HAVE A LIFE, YOU KNOW.

34:44.500 --> 34:46.000
YOU DO?

34:46.000 --> 34:49.458
JUST GIVE ME
YOUR BONE-MARROW DNA RESULTS.

34:49.458 --> 34:51.333
NO MATCHES.

34:51.333 --> 34:53.000
BIG SURPRISE.

34:53.000 --> 34:55.166
DO ME A FAVOR ON YOUR WAY OUT,
WILL YOU?

34:55.166 --> 34:57.458
DROP THESE DENTAL X-RAYS
AT THE FIELD MORGUE FOR ME?

34:57.458 --> 34:58.792
TECH SHOULD STILL BE THERE.

34:58.792 --> 35:00.291
FUCKING BAY HARBOR BUTCHER

35:00.291 --> 35:02.417
IS BUTCHERING
MY ONLINE SOCIAL LIFE.

35:05.083 --> 35:06.417
SORRY.

35:11.667 --> 35:13.208
NEXT.

35:19.583 --> 35:22.417
Matthews:
I FIGURED YOU'D STILL BE HERE.

35:22.417 --> 35:26.208
YOU WERE A PAIN IN THE ASS
BUT ALWAYS A DAMN HARD WORKER.

35:26.208 --> 35:29.250
AND, OF COURSE, YOU KNEW
HOW TO HANDLE THE PRESS.

35:31.250 --> 35:32.959
COME HERE A MINUTE.

35:44.125 --> 35:46.542
THE PUBLIC NEEDS TO BELIEVE
THAT WE CAN PROTECT THEM,

35:46.542 --> 35:48.959
OR ALL HELL BREAKS LOOSE,
SO I NEED ALL MY PEOPLE

35:48.959 --> 35:50.625
OPERATING AT THEIR
VERY HIGHEST LEVELS.

35:50.625 --> 35:52.542
I AGREE.

35:52.542 --> 35:54.333
SHOULD I BE WORRIED
ABOUT PASCAL?

35:55.792 --> 35:57.542
PASCAL?

35:57.542 --> 35:58.333
WHY?

35:59.959 --> 36:01.959
YOU CAN CUT THE CRAP, MARIA.

36:01.959 --> 36:04.542
I KNOW SHE'S BEEN AWOL
ON PERSONAL MATTERS.

36:04.542 --> 36:06.583
THE PRESS FUCKUP IS HUGE,

36:06.583 --> 36:09.834
AND NOW I'M BEGINNING TO HEAR
RUMORS ABOUT ERRATIC BEHAVIOR.

36:09.834 --> 36:11.959
AND YOU'RE ASKING ME
BECAUSE...

36:11.959 --> 36:13.583
BECAUSE YOU'VE DONE THE JOB.

36:13.583 --> 36:15.959
SO IF SHE'S OUT,
THAT MEANS YOU'RE BACK IN.

36:15.959 --> 36:20.333
THAT MAKES YOU HER HARSHEST
CRITIC, AND I WANT IT STRAIGHT.

36:20.333 --> 36:21.250
SO...

36:21.250 --> 36:23.542
TAKE YOUR SHOT, MARIA.

36:23.542 --> 36:25.458
HMM.

36:25.458 --> 36:27.333
YOU KNOW WHAT
"ERRATIC" MEANS?

36:28.417 --> 36:31.333
IT'S CODE FOR "NON-MALE,"

36:31.333 --> 36:34.125
AND IT'S THE SAME BULLSHIT
SEXISM I PUT UP WITH

36:34.125 --> 36:36.333
WHEN I WAS IN CHARGE.

36:36.333 --> 36:40.125
I WON'T DIGNIFY RUMORS, CAPTAIN.
PASCAL'S FINE.

36:48.709 --> 36:51.375
MINIVAN'S THAT WAY.

36:51.375 --> 36:54.208
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]
FIELD MORGUE'S THIS WAY.

36:54.208 --> 36:55.834
I'LL WAIT.

36:55.834 --> 36:58.333
YOU SHOULD TAKE THE NIGHT OFF,
SERGEANT.

36:58.333 --> 36:59.542
ON PIZZA NIGHT?

36:59.542 --> 37:02.125
NO WAY.

37:02.125 --> 37:04.000
WHAT DOES THAT GIRLFRIEND
OF YOURS SEE

37:04.000 --> 37:05.834
IN A FREAK SHOW LIKE YOU
ANYWAY?

37:05.834 --> 37:06.875
YOU HAVE TO ASK HER.

37:06.875 --> 37:08.208
MAYBE I WILL.

37:10.542 --> 37:12.333
[ SIGHS ]

37:14.083 --> 37:16.375
WHAT EXACTLY IS IT
YOU THINK I'VE DONE?

37:16.375 --> 37:18.750
I KNOW YOU'RE CONNECTED
TO THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

37:18.750 --> 37:20.917
COULD YOU BE MORE VAGUE?

37:20.917 --> 37:23.041
I KNOW YOU'RE TOO CAREFUL.

37:23.041 --> 37:24.375
YOU KEEP
YOUR ASSETS IN CASH.

37:24.375 --> 37:27.125
YOU DON'T BELONG TO ANY
ORGANIZATIONS OR ALUMNI GROUPS.

37:27.125 --> 37:28.875
YOU WERE TOP OF YOUR CLASS
IN MED SCHOOL,

37:28.875 --> 37:31.709
BUT YOU TRADED IT
FOR FUCKING BLOOD SPATTER.

37:31.709 --> 37:34.083
I KNOW YOU STUDIED MARTIAL ARTS
IN COLLEGE,

37:34.083 --> 37:37.750
BUT I DON'T KNOW WHAT A LAB GEEK
NEEDS WITH ADVANCED JUJITSU.

37:37.750 --> 37:40.250
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT AN EASY CREDIT IS?

37:40.250 --> 37:43.250
I KNOW
YOU'RE A GOOD LIAR, TOO.

37:47.709 --> 37:50.041
NOT GOOD ENOUGH.

38:05.208 --> 38:08.083
Dexter: SERGEANT DOAKES
THINKS HE KNOWS MY SECRETS,

38:08.083 --> 38:12.125
BUT HE ONLY NEEDS TO LOOK
AT THIS, MY BODY OF WORK,

38:12.125 --> 38:13.792
TO KNOW THE REAL ME.

38:13.792 --> 38:16.417
SUIT UP
IF YOU'RE GONNA TOUCH THEM.

38:17.625 --> 38:19.417
OH.

38:19.417 --> 38:23.959
NO, I'M JUST, UH...
DROPPING OFF SOME X-RAYS.

38:23.959 --> 38:25.625
I'M DEXTER MORGAN.

38:25.625 --> 38:27.667
I KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

38:27.667 --> 38:30.458
RIGHT.

38:30.458 --> 38:33.083
LOOKS LIKE THE LAB TECH'S
GONE HOME FOR THE NIGHT,

38:33.083 --> 38:36.625
SO I'LL JUST...

38:36.625 --> 38:39.417
[ SIGHS ]

38:40.875 --> 38:43.125
YOU HOPING
THEY'LL TALK TO YOU?

38:43.125 --> 38:44.917
THE ONES WITH HEADS,
ANYWAY.

38:47.166 --> 38:50.500
THEY ALWAYS SPEAK...
EVENTUALLY.

38:54.125 --> 38:57.667
JUST GOT TO ASK
THE RIGHT QUESTION.

38:57.667 --> 39:00.291
WHICH IS?

39:01.875 --> 39:03.458
"WHY WERE THEY CHOSEN?"

39:03.458 --> 39:06.667
YOU LOOKING FOR A PATTERN?

39:06.667 --> 39:08.500
ONE DOESN'T KILL
THIS MANY PEOPLE

39:08.500 --> 39:12.333
IN THIS CAREFUL, METHODICAL WAY
WITHOUT A REASON --

39:12.333 --> 39:14.375
SOME...

39:14.375 --> 39:16.375
TWISTED SET OF PRINCIPLES.

39:18.792 --> 39:21.417
YEAH, THEY WOULD HAVE TO BE
TWISTED, WOULDN'T THEY?

39:21.417 --> 39:23.667
THE WORST KILLERS IN HISTORY
ARE USUALLY THE ONES

39:23.667 --> 39:25.917
WHO THINK THEIR MURDERS
WERE SOMEHOW...JUST --

39:25.917 --> 39:28.458
EVEN DESERVED.

39:28.458 --> 39:30.417
LEADERS HAVE SLAUGHTERED
WHOLE POPULATIONS

39:30.417 --> 39:32.792
FOR THE SAME WARPED REASON.

39:33.834 --> 39:36.750
BUT THERE'S NEVER
ANY JUSTIFICATION FOR KILLING.

39:36.750 --> 39:38.959
NO.

39:38.959 --> 39:41.542
WELL, ONE, OF COURSE.

39:44.041 --> 39:46.166
TO SAVE AN INNOCENT LIFE.

39:48.000 --> 39:50.458
TO SAVE AN INNOCENT LIFE.

39:50.458 --> 39:52.417
HOW MANY MORE BODIES
WOULD THERE BE

39:52.417 --> 39:56.750
HAD I NOT STOPPED
THOSE KILLERS?

39:56.750 --> 39:59.125
I DIDN'T DO IT TO SAVE LIVES...

39:59.125 --> 40:02.542
BUT SAVE LIVES I DID.

40:02.542 --> 40:04.500
MOTIVATION ASIDE,

40:04.500 --> 40:09.041
I THINK HARRY AND LUNDY
WOULD AGREE ON THIS ONE.

40:15.333 --> 40:17.709
[ CAR ALARM CHIRPS ]

40:17.709 --> 40:19.208
Dexter:
ROGER THE ARTFUL DODGER.

40:19.208 --> 40:20.458
JESUS!

40:20.458 --> 40:22.291
YOU SCARED ME, BRO.

40:22.291 --> 40:24.375
WE HAVE
SOME UNFINISHED BUSINESS.

40:24.375 --> 40:26.417
OH, YEAH, RIGHT,
THE WARRANTY AND STUFF.

40:26.417 --> 40:28.375
LISTEN, UH...
I CAN'T WRITE YOU UP RIGHT NOW.

40:28.375 --> 40:29.959
I GOT THE WIFE
WAITING FOR ME.

40:29.959 --> 40:31.250
YOU'RE NOT MARRIED.

40:31.250 --> 40:32.417
EX-WIFE.
I GOT TO TAKE THE KIDS.

40:32.417 --> 40:34.834
YOU DON'T HAVE KIDS.
STEPKIDS -- THEY'RE HERS.

40:34.834 --> 40:35.417
NOPE.

40:35.417 --> 40:37.333
OKAY, HOW ABOUT THIS ONE?

40:37.333 --> 40:39.583
I DON'T GIVE A SHIT.

40:41.959 --> 40:44.375
NEITHER DO I.

40:52.875 --> 40:54.083
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

40:54.083 --> 40:56.583
YOU WERE RIGHT
ABOUT THE AMPLE CARGO SPACE.

41:13.291 --> 41:15.083
WHERE AM I?

41:20.000 --> 41:22.125
LOOKS DIFFERENT
UNDER PLASTIC,

41:22.125 --> 41:24.917
BUT YOU SPENT
AN EVENING HERE...

41:24.917 --> 41:27.583
WITH ANN COHEN.

41:27.583 --> 41:30.500
YOU TOOK HER LAST BREATH
FROM HER RIGHT OVER THERE.

41:30.500 --> 41:31.959
YOU REMEMBER?
NO.

41:31.959 --> 41:34.291
YOU'RE -- YOU'RE WRONG.
I WOULDN'T.

41:34.291 --> 41:37.125
YOU WOULD AND YOU DID AND
YOU WERE ABOUT TO DO IT AGAIN.

41:37.125 --> 41:38.083
THAT'S WHY WE'RE HERE.

41:38.083 --> 41:40.417
NO, THIS IS CRAZY.

41:40.417 --> 41:42.834
YOU GOT THE WRONG GUY.
I --

41:42.834 --> 41:44.417
I SELL CARS, FOR GOD'S SAKE.

41:44.417 --> 41:47.750
I'VE NEVER HURT ANYONE IN MY
LIFE -- DEFINITELY NOT A WOMAN.

41:47.750 --> 41:49.083
WHY CAN'T I DO THAT?

41:49.083 --> 41:50.166
DO WHAT?

41:50.166 --> 41:52.709
LIE LIKE THAT.

41:52.709 --> 41:56.625
I MEAN, I THOUGHT I WAS GOOD,
BUT YOU, IT'S...MWAH.

41:56.625 --> 41:58.041
I DON'T LIE.

41:58.041 --> 42:00.333
OKAY, THAT ONE WAS WEAK.

42:00.333 --> 42:03.959
OKAY, LOOK, ANY CAR ON THE LOT,
IT'S YOURS.

42:03.959 --> 42:07.333
T-BIRD, TOWN CAR, YOU NAME IT --
YOURS FREE.

42:07.333 --> 42:08.500
I'LL CALL IT IN RIGHT NOW.

42:08.500 --> 42:09.542
LOT'S CLOSED.

42:09.542 --> 42:11.834
I'LL HAVE THEM OPEN IT UP.
I'M THE MANAGER.

42:11.834 --> 42:13.625
THE MANAGER'S NAME
IS RICK BUXTON.

42:13.625 --> 42:15.125
YEAH, BUT I'VE BEEN THERE
LONGER THAN HE HAS.

42:15.125 --> 42:17.458
YOU'VE BEEN THERE
THREE MONTHS.
AT THE OTHER LOT.

42:17.458 --> 42:18.959
[ LAUGHS ]

42:20.583 --> 42:23.500
IT'S LIKE WATCHING SOMEONE
SKI MOGULS.

42:23.500 --> 42:25.542
YOU JUST HOP
FROM ONE LIE TO THE NEXT --

42:25.542 --> 42:27.166
NO SHAME, NO EMBARRASSMENT.

42:27.166 --> 42:30.375
YOU JUST DON'T GIVE A SHIT.

42:32.208 --> 42:33.542
THAT'S THE KEY, RIGHT?

42:33.542 --> 42:37.041
NOT TO CARE
ABOUT ANYONE OR ANYTHING.

42:37.041 --> 42:39.041
I CARE.

42:39.041 --> 42:41.208
I CARE A LOT.

42:41.208 --> 42:43.417
NO, IT WAS A COMPLIMENT.

42:43.417 --> 42:44.709
I DON'T CARE, EITHER.

42:44.709 --> 42:46.375
YES, YOU DO.

42:46.375 --> 42:48.000
LIKE ABOUT YOUR WIFE.

42:48.000 --> 42:49.125
NOT MARRIED.

42:49.125 --> 42:51.709
GIRLFRIEND, THEN.

42:51.709 --> 42:53.750
I SAW IT THE MINUTE
YOU WALKED ON THE LOT.

42:57.375 --> 43:00.208
WHAT DID YOU SEE?
TELL ME.

43:00.208 --> 43:04.333
LOOK, MOST GUYS YOUR AGE,
THEY BEELINE...

43:04.333 --> 43:05.667
RIGHT FOR THE HORSEPOWER --

43:05.667 --> 43:07.750
YOU KNOW,
SOMETHING FLASHY, SEXY.

43:07.750 --> 43:09.125
BUT YOU --

43:09.125 --> 43:12.667
YOU'RE THERE ALL ALONE,
NO ONE THERE TO NAG YOU,

43:12.667 --> 43:15.208
AND YOU DON'T EVEN GLANCE
AT THE COUPES.

43:15.208 --> 43:18.458
THE ONLY THING YOU LOOK AT
IS THE MINIVAN,

43:18.458 --> 43:22.333
LIKE YOU CAN SEE HER
IN THE PASSENGER'S SEAT

43:22.333 --> 43:23.583
AND THE KIDS IN THE BACK.

43:23.583 --> 43:25.834
LEAVE THE KIDS OUT.
SEE?

43:25.834 --> 43:28.750
YOU'RE LYING TO YOURSELF
IF YOU THINK YOU DON'T CARE.

43:31.083 --> 43:35.333
SHE'S JUST A COMPANION,
REALLY.

43:35.333 --> 43:37.041
STARTED THAT WAY,
ANYWAY.

43:37.041 --> 43:38.792
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

43:38.792 --> 43:41.375
SOMEONE WHO...

43:41.375 --> 43:43.291
LOOKED GOOD, NORMAL.

43:43.291 --> 43:45.041
THEY WORM THEIR WAY IN.

43:45.041 --> 43:47.333
YEAH, THEY DO.

43:47.333 --> 43:49.667
THEN THEY SHUT YOU OUT.

43:53.000 --> 43:54.834
[ SCOFFS ]

43:54.834 --> 43:57.583
THAT'S WHAT THIS IS ABOUT --
THAT SHE SHUT YOU OUT?

43:57.583 --> 44:00.208
OH.
MAN, OKAY, I GET IT.

44:00.208 --> 44:03.166
I-I -- I'VE BEEN THERE.

44:03.166 --> 44:04.458
[ SIGHS ]

44:04.458 --> 44:06.667
BUT YOU CAN'T LET HER
GET TO YOU LIKE THIS,

44:06.667 --> 44:09.333
'CAUSE -- 'CAUSE
THEY'RE ALL THE SAME --

44:09.333 --> 44:11.834
FUCKING BITCHES.

44:11.834 --> 44:14.542
YOU DO EVERYTHING FOR THEM,
AND THEN THEY FUCK YOU.

44:14.542 --> 44:15.875
SHE'S NOT WORTH IT,
ALL RIGHT?

44:15.875 --> 44:17.583
YOU'RE BETTER OFF
WITHOUT THAT CUNT.

44:17.583 --> 44:19.000
DON'T...

44:21.250 --> 44:23.125
...TALK THAT WAY
ABOUT MY GIRLFRIEND.

44:28.834 --> 44:33.458
Dexter: I'M DEXTER,
AND I'M NOT SURE WHAT I AM.

44:33.458 --> 44:35.834
All: HI, DEXTER.

44:35.834 --> 44:41.583
I JUST KNOW
THERE'S SOMETHING DARK IN ME...

44:41.583 --> 44:43.667
AND I HIDE IT.

44:45.875 --> 44:48.875
I CERTAINLY
DON'T TALK ABOUT IT...

44:48.875 --> 44:51.625
BUT IT'S THERE...

44:51.625 --> 44:52.792
ALWAYS.

44:55.458 --> 44:57.583
THIS DARK PASSENGER.

44:57.583 --> 45:02.208
AND WHEN HE'S DRIVING,
I FEEL...

45:02.208 --> 45:05.333
ALIVE...

45:05.333 --> 45:09.625
HALF SICK WITH THE THRILL
OF COMPLETE WRONGNESS.

45:12.166 --> 45:13.959
I DON'T FIGHT HIM.

45:13.959 --> 45:15.417
I DON'T WANT TO.

45:17.875 --> 45:21.542
HE'S ALL I'VE GOT.

45:21.542 --> 45:23.208
NOTHING ELSE COULD LOVE ME,

45:23.208 --> 45:25.667
NOT EVEN...

45:27.208 --> 45:29.041
...ESPECIALLY NOT ME.

45:32.792 --> 45:37.333
OR IS THAT JUST A LIE
THE DARK PASSENGER TELLS ME?

45:40.917 --> 45:44.917
BECAUSE LATELY THERE ARE
THESE MOMENTS WHEN I FEEL...

45:50.333 --> 45:54.959
...CONNECTED
TO SOMETHING ELSE -- SOMEONE.

45:58.083 --> 46:01.291
IT'S LIKE...

46:01.291 --> 46:04.291
THE MASK IS SLIPPING...

46:06.959 --> 46:09.041
...AND THINGS...

46:12.083 --> 46:15.750
...PEOPLE...

46:15.750 --> 46:18.792
WHO NEVER MATTERED BEFORE
ARE SUDDENLY STARTING TO MATTER.

46:20.959 --> 46:23.917
IT SCARES THE HELL OUT OF ME.

46:27.208 --> 46:29.291
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

46:51.542 --> 46:53.542
HELLO...

46:53.542 --> 46:54.959
DEXTER.

47:03.125 --> 47:06.834
Man: THAT'S ALL THE TIME
WE HAVE FOR SHARING.

47:06.834 --> 47:11.333
WOULD SOMEONE LEAD US
IN THE SERENITY PRAYER?

47:11.333 --> 47:13.291
LILA.

47:27.250 --> 47:29.625
I KNEW THERE
WAS SOMETHING WRONG WITH YOU.

47:29.625 --> 47:33.500
THE SECRETS,
THE SNEAKING AROUND --

47:33.500 --> 47:35.500
NOW IT ALL MAKES SENSE.

47:35.500 --> 47:38.333
All: GOD GRANT ME
SERENITY TO ACCEPT...

47:38.333 --> 47:41.667
A LOT OF COPS
HAVE BEEN WHERE YOU ARE.

47:41.667 --> 47:44.000
THE BOOZE, THE DRUGS...

47:44.000 --> 47:46.458
MAKES THE JOB GO DOWN EASIER.

47:49.000 --> 47:52.625
STAY CLEAN AND STAY OUT OF
MY WAY, WE WON'T HAVE A PROBLEM.

47:53.917 --> 47:57.333
OH, AND YOU OWE ME A NEW
MICHELIN, YOU MOTHERFUCKER.

47:57.333 --> 47:58.875
[ APPLAUSE ]

48:07.208 --> 48:08.709
I HAVE ALL YOUR FORMS,

48:08.709 --> 48:11.041
SO WE'LL DO WHAT WE CAN
TO BRING YOUR DAD HOME.

48:11.041 --> 48:13.250
I'M SORRY.
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

48:13.250 --> 48:15.291
I DON'T WANT HIM HOME.

48:15.291 --> 48:17.875
JUST TELL ME HE'S DEAD.
WE NEED TO KNOW HE'S GONE.

48:17.875 --> 48:20.709
RIGHT, YOU WANT CLOSURE.

48:20.709 --> 48:22.667
I WANT PEACE.

48:22.667 --> 48:24.375
HE MADE OUR LIVES
A LIVING HELL.

48:24.375 --> 48:27.083
WHEN HE'D GO TO PRISON,
IT WAS A BLESSING, BUT, UH...

48:27.083 --> 48:30.041
YOU KEPT LETTING HIM OUT.

48:30.041 --> 48:32.667
I NEED TO TELL
MY MOTHER, MY SISTER

48:32.667 --> 48:35.333
THAT THEY'RE SAFE
AND THAT HE'S ROTTING IN HELL.

48:35.333 --> 48:37.834
CALL ME
WHEN YOU CAN TELL ME THAT.

48:52.375 --> 48:54.875
LUNDY, WAIT.

48:54.875 --> 48:57.250
UH...

48:57.250 --> 49:00.625
I THINK -- I MEAN,
IT COULD BE A COINCIDENCE --

49:00.625 --> 49:01.792
BUT THERE ARE TWO OF THEM.

49:01.792 --> 49:03.792
TWO...

49:03.792 --> 49:06.709
MISSING PEOPLE WITH RECORDS --
PRISON RECORDS.

49:08.583 --> 49:10.083
INTERESTING.

49:11.959 --> 49:15.458
AND WHO TYPICALLY HAS
A PRISON RECORD?

49:17.333 --> 49:20.291
I DON'T KNOW.

49:20.291 --> 49:21.583
BAD GUYS?

49:22.959 --> 49:24.125
BAD GUYS.

49:25.458 --> 49:26.792
DO YOU THINK
IT COULD BE A --

49:26.792 --> 49:29.000
A PATTERN?
MAYBE.

49:30.125 --> 49:32.667
WE'LL RUN ALL THE VICTIMS' DNA
AGAINST THE CRIMINAL DATABASE.

49:32.667 --> 49:34.500
D.C. LAB IS STILL OPEN.

49:36.709 --> 49:38.625
COME ON.
LET'S GET TO WORK.

49:41.583 --> 49:43.500
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

49:53.542 --> 49:54.875
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

49:54.875 --> 49:56.333
DEXTER, WHAT?

49:56.333 --> 49:57.375
YOU WERE RIGHT.

49:57.375 --> 49:59.166
I'M SORRY TO WAKE YOU UP,

49:59.166 --> 50:01.125
BUT I HAD TO LET YOU KNOW
THAT YOU WERE RIGHT.

50:01.125 --> 50:02.333
ABOUT WHAT?

50:02.333 --> 50:04.166
THE PROGRAM.

50:04.166 --> 50:06.542
[ Laughing ] IT'S...

50:06.542 --> 50:10.125
IT'S GOOD.
IT'S REALLY GOOD.

50:10.125 --> 50:14.834
I...
AM ALWAYS SO IN MY HEAD.

50:14.834 --> 50:18.041
BUT THIS -- IT WAS...

50:18.041 --> 50:19.500
GOOD.

50:19.500 --> 50:21.709
[ CHUCKLES ]

50:21.709 --> 50:23.875
IN FACT,
IT'S ALREADY HELPED ME A LOT.

50:23.875 --> 50:25.166
THANK YOU.

50:25.166 --> 50:26.500
OH.

50:26.500 --> 50:28.875
[ CHUCKLES ]

50:28.875 --> 50:31.041
MMM.

50:38.208 --> 50:40.667
OH, I DO LOVE THIS CAR.

50:40.667 --> 50:42.500
YEAH, I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT.

50:42.500 --> 50:43.792
[ CHUCKLES ]

50:46.834 --> 50:49.041
SO, I WILL PICK YOU UP
IN AN HOUR.

50:49.041 --> 50:52.166
WE'LL GO SOMEPLACE NICE
FOR LUNCH.

50:52.166 --> 50:54.250
OH, THERE'S MY SPONSOR.

50:54.250 --> 50:55.417
REALLY? WHERE?

50:55.417 --> 50:57.750
THE GUY IN THE BLUE SHIRT?

50:57.750 --> 50:59.583
NO, NEXT TO HIM -- LILA.

51:05.625 --> 51:06.625
HUH.

51:06.625 --> 51:07.875
BYE.

51:07.875 --> 51:09.041
BYE.

51:13.667 --> 51:16.917
I'M BACK.
[ CHUCKLES ]
